ScanExperiment¶

Experiment code to scan a parameter that is controlled by the FPGA.

The Pulse Program for each point od the scan, the Pulse Program receives the address and value of the scanned parameter on its pipe input. It is expected to echo those on the pipe output followed by the measurement results. It is expected to send an endlabel (0xffffffff) when finished.
